                                <property name="label" translatable="yes">&lt;big&gt;&lt;b&gt;Custom state object on contracts&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/big&gt;
main purpose of state objects is giving possibility of static state binding (visibility/sensitivity) and completely remove all need to
track which source is now active. State object refreshes whenever either source in application. changes or notification for one of 
